INSTALL

To uncompress and install on a Unix-like system, do this:

~~~~
tar xvzf quoter*tar.gz
cd quoter*

make && make install
~~~~

On MacOS replace "make" with "make LEXLIB=l".



USAGE

 It's a filter.  You can use it like this:

 quoter < stuff.html > stuff.wiki


NOTES

  I have some test files.  "test.html" is a normal HTML file;
  "micro-test.html" is an HTML file generated by Microsoft Word.


